CliffsComplete combines the full original text of The Taming of the Shrew with a helpful glossary and CliffsNotes-quality commentary into one volume. You will find:A unique pedagogical approach that combines the complete original text with expert commentary following each sceneA descriptive bibliography and historical background on the author, the times, and the work itselfAn improved character map that graphically illustrates the relationships among the charactersSidebar glossaries"', 'A comedic play by Shakespeare about a man’s attempt to tame a headstrong woman in a tale of courtship and gender roles.', NULL, '074347757X', '9780743477574', 304, NULL, 3480, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13233287-L.jpg', '/works/OL362690W', NULL, 'January 1, 2004', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'the-taming-of-the-shrew-william-shakespeare', 1, 'openlibrary', NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-17 23:33:56', '2026-03-22 03:34:49');
